In the House;;2012;;R;;Drama,Mystery,Thriller;;7.4;;François Ozon;;Fabrice Luchini,Vincent Schmitt,Ernst Umhauer,Kristin Scott Thomas,Emmanuelle Seigner,Denis Ménochet,Bastien Ughetto,Jean-François Balmer,Yolande Moreau,Catherine Davenier,Jacques Bosc,Stéphanie Campion,Diana Stewart,Ronny Pong,Jana Bittnerová,Nadir Azni,Bénérice Barbin,Marie Brunet;;A sixteen-year-old boy insinuates himself into the house of a fellow student from his literature class and writes about it in essays for his French teacher. Faced with this gifted and unusual pupil, the teacher rediscovers his enthusiasm for his work, but the boy's intrusion will unleash a series of uncontrollable events.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1964624/